title: FS: 84 card T205 Starter Set *** sold
author: jasonc

posts.post_title: FS: 84 card T205 Starter Set *** sold
posts.post_content:
At this point, I do enjoy collecting both the T205's and T206's, but found out 
cost-wise it would be expensive to try and go for both sets, so I am 
parting with my T205's. I am preferring the T206's, and for the T205's, I don't have any of the real big cards.  I am open to a trade or 
cash/trade for T206's 
(Please see below)

*** STARTER SET HAS BEEN SOLD ***


All low grade cards, backs overall are decent, with a majority of the cards 
showing legible text --Still, it's a partial set for somebody that is not 
concerned with condition.
